article.headline: Hubbard's 15 lead Western Michigan over Eastern Michigan 73-56

images.name: Eastern Michigan Eagles vs. Western Michigan Broncos: Full Highlights
images.caption: Eastern Michigan Eagles vs. Western Michigan Broncos: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Hubbard's 15 lead Western Michigan over Eastern Michigan 73-56
article.story: KALAMAZOO, Mich. -- — Seth Hubbard's 15 points helped Western Michigan defeat Eastern Michigan 73-56 on Tuesday night. Hubbard shot 6 for 10, including 3 for 6 from beyond the arc for the Broncos (8-11, 5-2 Mid-American Conference). B. Artis White scored 13 points, going 5 of 8 (3 for 4 from 3-point range). Anthony Crump was 4 of 6 shooting and 2 of 5 from the free throw line to finish with 10 points. Tyson Acuff led the way for the Eagles (8-11, 1-6) with 14 points and four assists. Jalin Billingsley added 11 points and seven rebounds for Eastern Michigan. In addition, Yusuf Jihad had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
